The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                                       7                                                                                      IN THE CITY
                  
	Aryan defeated Peerless 3-0 in the CFL Premier Division on Thursday. While Babatunde struck twice, Stanley scored the other goal. The match between Eastern Railway and Port Trust ended goalless.          
	 Mohun Bagan is all set to sign Okwy Okonkwo Diamondstar as the fourth foreigner in their squad. The Australian has been training with the side for the last three days, in Siliguri, where the Bagan residential camp is being held. Though coach Stanley Rozario is yet to give his nod to Okwy officially, club sources say that the tall defender has been impressive in practice.       
	Jose Baretto, Edeh Chidi and Murithala Ali are the other three foreign recruits of Bagan.                
	 Newly-promoted CFL Premier Division club Southern Samity are mulling to sign Liberain striker Theodore Sunday for the season. Sunday, who is currently in the US, would arrive in the city by August 31, informed a club official. Meanwhile, the club announced on Thursday that Haldia-based company Five Star will be the team sponsor.          
	 Former AIFF secretary Asoke Ghosh passed away at his residence Thursday morning. Ghosh 78, suffered a massive cardiac arrest. He is survived by wife, son and daughter. Ghosh was also at the helm of Bengal Olympic Association (BOA) for two decades (1984-2004).                 
	 Mari Arul S of Southern Railway won the 23rd All India Railway Chess Championship, which concluded at the Khudiram Anushilan Kendra, on Thursday. Arul finished with 7.5 points. The team championship was won by Western Railway.                
	Football: CFL Premier Division: Southern Samity vs Kalighat MS (Salt Lake Stadium, 3:30 pm)                                                                                                                                                      
